name: Pecking Order
description: Choices.  Impacts.  There is more to think about than art.  And art is not the reason we engage.  Art is just how we speak.  And show the things we can't say.  I knew it would be complicated.  But, I never knew deep choices would come so soon.  So fast.  But, the message must be set free.  Choices. Impacts. Liberty.
